{"article_id":"quGGXGsSnMCAqSa2","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"House Republicans ' effort","depth":7},{"id":1,"text":"to ' repeal and replace ' Obamacare","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"fell through on Friday ,","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"but the White House ' s ambitious agenda is still alive .","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"Up next :","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"Tax reform .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"Speaking Friday at a Washington event","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"hosted by news site Axios ,","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"Treasury Secretary Steven Mnuchin said","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"he expected the White House to release its tax plan \" pretty soon. \"","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"The plan ,","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"he indicated ,","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"is the culmination of two months ' work","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"that has looked at a range of possible tax scenarios .","depth":9},{"id":14,"text":"Though the details still remain to be hammered out in consultation with Congress ,","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"the stated goal is to cut federal tax rates for middle-income Americans .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"Secretary Mnuchin ' s signature policy calls for wealthy Americans to continue paying the same level of taxes ,","depth":6},{"id":17,"text":"though an end to certain deductions would mean the tax burden would be distributed differently ,","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"something","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"he called a \" goal \" on Friday .","depth":8},{"id":20,"text":"President Trump , meanwhile , has long promised a cut in the corporate tax rate from 35 percent to 15 percent .","depth":4},{"id":21,"text":"The failure","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"to reform healthcare ,","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"observers caution ,","depth":7},{"id":24,"text":"might limit the possibilities of a tax overhaul .","depth":5},{"id":25,"text":"The two are linked , and not just politically .","depth":6},{"id":26,"text":"But Mnuchin suggests","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"that tax reform would fare better than healthcare ,","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"describing it as a more straightforward issue","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"and citing bipartisan support for a simplified tax code .","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"`` We 're able to take the tax code and redesign things ,","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"and I think","depth":12},{"id":32,"text":"there is very , very strong support , ''","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"Mnuchin said","depth":11},{"id":34,"text":"before the healthcare reform vote was canceled ,","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"The Hill reported .","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"\" I think","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"in healthcare , it 's [ a ] much , much more complicated issue ,","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"where you start out with ObamaCare ,","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"which had all these issues ,","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"and you 're trying to kind of get rid of it","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"and make changes simultaneously . ''","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"In contrast to Obamacare , both parties agree","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"that the tax code is broken ,","depth":11},{"id":44,"text":"and that something needs to be done","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"to fix it .","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"But exactly what shape these reforms should take is heavily debated .","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"That ' s why ,","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"even though comprehensive tax reform was been a target of both the George W. Bush and Obama administrations ,","depth":11},{"id":49,"text":"both ultimately settled for more modest changes .","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"In fact , an overhaul on the scale","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"sought by the Trump administration","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"has not passed since 1986 .","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"But the White House appears unwilling to settle for less than complete reform .","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"The tax code is one of Mr. Trump ' s top issues ,","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"and Mnuchin indicated Friday","depth":10},{"id":56,"text":"that piecemeal changes would be insufficient .","depth":10},{"id":57,"text":"`` We are not cutting this up","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"and doing little pieces at a time , ''","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"Mnuchin said ,","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"according to the Associated Press .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"But","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"given the political setback on healthcare reform ,","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"comprehensive tax reform may no longer be possible ,","depth":12},{"id":64,"text":"some observers say .","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"Infrastructure reform may have been jeopardized , too .","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"`` The defeat of health care reconciliation threatens to derail the entire Trump economic plan .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"Period , \"","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"Steve Bell , a longtime staffer on the Senate Budget Committee and now an economic policy advisor at the Bipartisan Policy Center in Washington , D.C. , told CNN Money .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"Congressional Republicans had expected to use the $ 1 trillion in saved Obamacare taxes","depth":6},{"id":70,"text":"to help finance tax cuts ,","depth":7},{"id":71,"text":"which was part of the reason","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"healthcare reform was attempted before tax reform .","depth":8},{"id":73,"text":"Without those funds ,","depth":6},{"id":74,"text":"it may become harder to sell Congress on tax reductions .","depth":6},{"id":75,"text":"But others remain optimistic .","depth":5},{"id":76,"text":"Speak","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"ng after the healthcare vote was cancelled on Friday ,","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"ouse Speaker Paul Ryan","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"R )","depth":12},{"id":80,"text":"f Wisconsin said","depth":11},{"id":81,"text":"he reform agenda was still on course .","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"This does make tax reform more difficult ,","depth":10},{"id":83,"text":"ut it does not in any way make it impossible , \"","depth":10},{"id":84,"text":"e said at a news conference ,","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"olitico reported .","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"We will proceed with tax reform . \"","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"aving lost one key battle ,","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"yan added ,","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"ay have given congressional Republicans greater impetus","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"o win the tax reform fight .","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"Every man and woman in this conference is motivated more than ever to step up our game , \"","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"e said ,","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"NN Money reported .","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"embers of the House Ways and Means Committee ,","depth":5},{"id":95,"text":"hich is responsible for writing tax legislation ,","depth":5},{"id":96,"text":"re ready to get started .","depth":4},{"id":97,"text":"et the Monitor Stories","depth":6},{"id":98,"text":"ou care about","depth":6},{"id":99,"text":"elivered to your inbox .","depth":5},{"id":100,"text":"y signing up ,","depth":5},{"id":101,"text":"ou agree to our Privacy Policy","depth":5},{"id":102,"text":"Tuesday morning is our first tax reform meeting , \"","depth":4},{"id":103,"text":"ommittee member Kenny Marchant","depth":6},{"id":104,"text":"R )","depth":6},{"id":105,"text":"f Texas told Politico .","depth":5},{"id":106,"text":"nuchin said","depth":5},{"id":107,"text":"e hoped","depth":6},{"id":108,"text":"he tax overhaul would be completed before Congress ' August recess .","depth":6},{"id":109,"text":"f not ,","depth":6},{"id":110,"text":"e added ,","depth":6},{"id":111,"text":"t would \" absolutely \" be done in the fall .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":223,"left":205,"right":222,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":205,"left":132,"right":204,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":117,"right":131,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":117,"left":115,"right":116,"rela